The Task Create a static single page application using React. You can use any modern React framework, such as Next.JS or CRA It should have a home page that tells us a bit about yourself and why you want to be a developer at SovTech. Feel free to express yourself in the design. Think of this task as creating a mini-portfolio page. The Requirements: It should be deployed using a simple static site hosting service, such as Vercel, Netlify etc. Your code should be pushed to a public repository on Github with an updated Readme. The Readme should contain a guide on how to bootstrap the app and a link do the deployed version.
